        <div class="columnLeft section">
            <h2 class="section">Modernized Royalty Framework</h2>
            <p>The <a href="/Org/pdfs/RoyaltyReportJan2016.pdf" title="link to the report in PDF" target="_blank">royalty review is complete</a><img alt="" title="PDF icon" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;" src="/Org/graphics/Icon_acrobat.gif" />
. Read about the <a href="http://www.alberta.ca/royalties.cfm" title="link to royalties on Alberta.ca" target="_blank">new royalty framework</a>. Technical information is also <a href="/About_Us/Royalty.asp" title="link to the royalty section complete with formulas in this site">available</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="columnRight section">
            <h2 class="section">Fort MacMurray evacuees</h2>
            <p>The <a href="http://www.ucahelps.alberta.ca/help.aspx" title="link to UCA helps information for evacuees" target="_blank">Utilities Consumer Advocate office</a> offers emergency and financial information.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
        </div>
<br />
        <div class="columnLeft section">
            <h2 class="section">Climate Leadership Plan</h2>
             <p>Under the purview of <a href="http://aep.alberta.ca/" title="link to Environment and Parks" target="_blank">Environment and Parks</a>, Albertas <a href="http://alberta.ca/climate/" title="link to the Climate Leadership Plan on Alberta.ca" target="_blank">Climate Leadership Plan</a> will protect the provinces health, environment and economy, and contribute to a more sustainable future.</p>
<p> </p>
        </div>
        <div class="columnRight section">
            <h2 class="section">Budget 2016</h2>
            <p><a href="http://www.alberta.ca/budget.cfm" title="Link to the 2016 Budget site " target="_blank"><img style="float: left;" alt="2016 Budget logo" src="/images/about/GOA-4854_170x100_JobsPlan_WebBanner.jpg" />
</a><br />
Budget was <br />
released <br />
April 14th.
</p>
<p> </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
