            <h2 class="section">Programs and Services</h2>
            <div class="columnLeft">
                <h3><a href="/About_Us/1014.asp">Resources in Alberta</a></h3>
                    <p><a href="/coal/coal.asp">Coal</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/minerals/minerals.asp">Minerals</a>, <a href="/NaturalGas/Gas.asp">Natural Gas</a>, <a href="/Oil/Oil.asp">Oil</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/OilSands/oilsands.asp">Oil Sands</a>&nbsp;<br />
and&nbsp;<a href="/OurBusiness/3697.asp" title="link to unconventional resources in this site">Unconventional resources</a>&nbsp;are found in Alberta. <a href="/Electricity/536.asp">Electricity</a>&nbsp;and <a href="/BioEnergy/bioenergy.asp" title="link to alternative energy in this site">Alternative and&nbsp;Renewable energy</a> use resources and waste biomass.</p>
    
                <h3><a href="/OurBusiness/1060.asp">People Services</a></h3>
                    
        <a  target="_blank" href="http://www.ucahelps.gov.ab.ca/4.html">Utilities Consumer Advocate</a>, <a  title="link to pricing and consumer information" href="/Electricity/679.asp">Electricity Pricing and consumer information</a> and the <a  href="/OurBusiness/1072.asp#Sales">Sales Results Map</a>
    

                    
            </div>
