<em>Royalty</em> - <a href="/coal/528.asp">Coal</a>, <a href="/minerals/546.asp">Minerals</a>, <a href="/NaturalGas/731.asp">Natural Gas</a>, <a href="/Oil/1926.asp" title="link to all the oil Royalty calculators">Oil Royalty Calculators</a>, <a href="/OilSands/584.asp">Oil Sands</a><br />
